## PreflightTest.getLatestSample() method

Get the latest stats sample generated by the PreflightTest.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getLatestSample(): Promise<PreflightTest.RTCSample>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;[PreflightTest.RTCSample](./voice-react-native-sdk.preflighttest_namespace.rtcsample_interface.md)<!-- -->&gt;

A Promise that - Resolves with the last [PreflightTest.RTCSample](./voice-react-native-sdk.preflighttest_namespace.rtcsample_interface.md) generated by the PreflightTest. - Resolves with `undefined` if there is no previously generated sample. - Rejects if the native layer encountered an error.
